01)Projection: lag(stock_price.price) ORDER BY [stock_price.price_date ASC NULLS LAST] ROWS BETWEEN UNBOUNDED PRECEDING AND UNBOUNDED FOLLOWING AS prev_price, lead(stock_price.price) ORDER BY [stock_price.price_date ASC NULLS LAST] ROWS BETWEEN UNBOUNDED PRECEDING AND UNBOUNDED FOLLOWING AS next_price, first_value(stock_price.price) PARTITION BY [__mr_match_number] ORDER BY [stock_price.price_date ASC NULLS LAST, __mr_match_number ASC NULLS LAST] ROWS BETWEEN UNBOUNDED PRECEDING AND UNBOUNDED FOLLOWING AS first_price
02)--Filter: __mr_is_last_match_row
03)----Projection: __mr_is_last_match_row, lag(stock_price.price) ORDER BY [stock_price.price_date ASC NULLS LAST] ROWS BETWEEN UNBOUNDED PRECEDING AND UNBOUNDED FOLLOWING, lead(stock_price.price) ORDER BY [stock_price.price_date ASC NULLS LAST] ROWS BETWEEN UNBOUNDED PRECEDING AND UNBOUNDED FOLLOWING, first_value(stock_price.price) PARTITION BY [__mr_match_number] ORDER BY [stock_price.price_date ASC NULLS LAST, __mr_match_number ASC NULLS LAST] ROWS BETWEEN UNBOUNDED PRECEDING AND UNBOUNDED FOLLOWING
