# Test no MEASURES clause
query TT
EXPLAIN SELECT * FROM stock_price
MATCH_RECOGNIZE (
    PARTITION BY company
    ORDER BY price_date
    PATTERN (A)
    DEFINE A AS price > 100
)
----
logical_plan
01)Projection: stock_price.company
02)--Filter: __mr_is_last_match_row
03)----Projection: stock_price.company, __mr_is_last_match_row
04)------MatchRecognizePattern: partition_by=[stock_price.company] order_by=[stock_price.price_date ASC NULLS LAST] pattern=[A]
05)--------Projection: stock_price.company, stock_price.price_date, stock_price.price, stock_price.price > Int32(100) AS __mr_symbol_A
06)----------TableScan: stock_price projection=[company, price_date, price]
